{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ce111c903d","title":"致教师代表大会","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bd30797e49","index":0,"year":1925,"month":1,"day":6,"articleId":"ce111c903d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"de24acabe4","type":"paragraph","text":"致教师代表大会","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"},{"id":"928e6a2d1a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九二五年一月六日）","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"},{"id":"eaf9b0db59","type":"paragraph","text":"人民教师的队伍是我国正在按社会主义原则建设新生活的劳动大军中的一个最必需的部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"},{"id":"be58fa86c4","type":"paragraph","text":"只有十百万劳动农民群众紧随着工人阶级前进，工人阶级坚定不移地领导劳动群众，工人阶级走向社会主义的道路才能是一条胜利的道路。","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"},{"id":"f45ba86a43","type":"paragraph","text":"乡村教师应当知道，没有这样的领导，就不可能有无产阶级专政，而没有这样的专政，我国就不可能成为一个自由独立的国家。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"},{"id":"b85e809e0e","type":"paragraph","text":"要成为一个连接农民群众和工人阶级的环节，一一这就是乡村教师的主要任务，如果他们真正愿意为本国人民的事业、为人民的自由独立的事业服务的话","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"},{"id":"80613c7ae6","type":"paragraph","text":"约·斯天林","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"},{"id":"9553b0aed8","type":"paragraph","text":"一九二五年一月六日载于一九二五年一月十日","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"},{"id":"126ea0a8b0","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"},{"id":"88dabf365c","type":"paragraph","text":"第7卷第4页“教师报”第二号","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d"}],"page":{"id":"283bfbaf23","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"ce111c903d","start":785,"end":785}}}},"__N_SSG":true}